Package: hunspell
Type: Package
Title: Hunspell Spell Checker
Version: 1.0.9000
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: A spell checker and morphological analyzer library
    designed for languages with rich morphology and complex word
    compounding or character encoding.
